Find out about events, programme listings and new online material from the World War One season at the BBC with our email newsletter. 
 You'll receive a confirmation email shortly. You need to reply to this email to start receiving the newsletter.
 Your personal information will be held by the BBC and will only be used in relation to this newsletter. Your details will not be passed to any third party without your consent. You will be given the opportunity to unsubscribe from each newsletter every time you receive it. Please visit the BBC's Privacy &amp; Cookies Policy for more information.
